question: I've been cramping real bad and having severe headaches.  I have a history of preeclampsia with my previous pregnancies so I went to the ER to find out I have placenta previa at 16 weeks, already spilling protein in my urine and I have group b strep. Im on bed rest and freaking out. They wanna watch me until birth if my 20 week ultrasound shows that my placenta is still low.
title: Nervousness!
